item.title: Dr.Kamal Poddar
item.description: MD Medicine, M.R.C.P(UK), M.B.B.S He is a specialist of Medicine, Nerves, Sugar, Thyroid, Gas, Pressure, Heart and Breathing. He is available on every Sunday at 12:30pm.

item.title: Dr.S.S.Nayak
item.description: M.B.B.S, M.S(ORTHO), DNB(ORTHO), MCH(ORTHO), MNAMS, FIJR He is a renowned Orthopedic(Bone Specialist) and Surgeon in Cuttack. He is available on every 15 days from 11/05/2023 on Thursday at 12:00pm.

item.title: Dr.N.K.Panigrahi
item.description: M.B.B.S, M.S(ORTHO) He is a renowned Orthopedic(Bone Specialist) and Surgeon in Bhubaneswar. He is available on every 15 days from 19/05/2023 on Friday at 10:00am.

item.title: Dr.Debadutta Senapati
item.description: M.S, MCH(NEUROSURGERY) He is a renowned Neurologist and Surgeon in Cuttack. He is available on Sundays of second and fourth weeks from 14/05/2023 at 6:00pm.

item.title: Dr.Arun Kumar Adak
item.description: M.B.B.S(CAL), MD(Paediatrics)(WBUHS), PGPN (Boston, USA), IPPN (Australia) He is a former and renowned neonatologist and paediatrician at Vellore CMCH. He is available on every Saturday at 4:30pm.

item.title: Dr.Tanmoy Sarkar
item.description: M.B.B.S, M.S, DNB He is an Ear, Nose and Throat Specialist and Surgeon at Debra Super Speciality Hospital. He is available on every Wednesday and Thursday at 2:00pm.

item.title: Dr.Rinku Biswas
item.description: M.B.B.S, D.N.B.P.G.T(OBS & Gynae) She is an Obstetrician and Gynecologist. She is available on every Saturday at 5:00pm.

item.title: Dr.Divyandu Vikas Bhanja
item.description: M.B.B.S(Cal), MD (Cal) He is a renowned Dermatoveneritis and Leproy Specialist. He is available on every Saturday at 2:30pm.
